    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you won't find a single flaw on this beauty\u2014it looks and feels like it literally just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away and spotless. It runs like a total dream and still has that fresh car feel. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. Feel free to drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis is mechanically superlative; the VANOS system has been comprehensively overhauled, rod bearings have been addressed, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014eliminating the common failure points of this platform. The factory-correct limited-slip differential provides exceptional torque vectoring, while the suspension maintains its original geometric integrity for a pure analog feel. Every seal is tight, the valvetrain is whisper-quiet, and the exterior retains a flawless deep luster. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the true enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
